name: Görgei The Chemist
description:
Generative input mixed with a photo taken in 2019 of the equestrian statue of Gorgey Artur on the Castle Hill of Budapest.

Görgei was a talented chemist, a successful general and one of the greatest military genius of the Hungarian Revolutionary Army, he was the leader of the victorious Glorious Spring Campaign liberating almost all of Western Hungary from Austrian occupation.
